Class AbstractImManagerConfigurationEntryHandler<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.im.loader.simple.AbstractImManagerConfigurationEntryHandler<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the loadable type (e.g. IMC or IMV)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationEntryHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultImcManagerConfigurationEntryHandler, DefaultImvManagerConfigurationEntryHandler

    public abstract class AbstractImManagerConfigurationEntryHandler<T>
extends Object
implements ConfigurationEntryHandler
    Generic configuration entry handler base to handle changes of configuration entries to load IM(C/V). Especially important for inheritance.
